deck: An aggressive school bully who often annoys and attempts to intimidate others.
description:
Origin

Taylor is a fifth grade student who attends Birch Elementary school in Long Island. She is aggressive, and bullies other students, including the anti-social but gentle student Barbara and the kind and lively student Sophia.

Creation

Taylor was created by writer Joe Kelly and artist JM Ken Niimura for the Image published mini series I Kill Giants. Taylor appears in the second issue.
